title: Poser ~ DAZ3D : 20 Low Rez Vehicles [RO 102050]
description:
Contents
 - 20 vehicles: trucks, bus, van, police car, cars, etc... props (.PP2 + .OBJ)
 - UV mapped textures 1024x1024 + templates

 BONUS FOR CUSTOMERS WHO BOUGHT POWERTOWN:
 Load 60 vehicles with a simple double click in the city. Automatically placed in the streets and car parks.

 NOTE:
 Vehicles are designed for use in a large urban scene with a general camera view. Avoid close-ups render, low polycount, the vehicles can be used in a video game engine.
 The level of detail is not high enough for that, hight polys vehicles are available in the market and in our store for close-ups renders (like: road Royds, el camino, etc ...).
